title: Monthly Wellness AMA
description: Join our expert panel for a monthly Ask Me Anything session focused on wellness strategies for rare disease patients. Our healthcare professionals will answer your questions live.

title: Caregiver Circle Support Group
description: A safe space for caregivers to share experiences, seek advice, and find support from others who understand the journey. Both in-person and virtual attendance options available.

title: Rare Disease Awareness Walk 2025
description: Join us for our annual awareness walk to support rare disease research and community building. Family-friendly event with activities, food vendors, and educational booths.

title: Understanding Sjögren's Disease Webinar
description: An educational webinar covering the latest research, treatment options, and management strategies for Sjögren's Disease. Featuring Dr. Emily Chen, rheumatologist.

title: New Member Orientation
description: Welcome session for new members of the Winsights Life community. Learn about platform features, support resources, and how to connect with others on similar journeys.

title: Mental Health & Chronic Illness Workshop
description: Interactive workshop addressing the mental health challenges faced by patients and caregivers. Includes coping strategies, mindfulness exercises, and Q&A with a licensed therapist.
